About Trader 2

Trader 2 uses patterns to estimate 12 months target price.

It analyses ~500 stock symbols trading in Australia and United States

The longest holding period is 365 days; Sell when estimated price or date reached, whichever comes first.

I use GitHub to timestamp every estimate as Proof of Existence. All archives is available here.

This page is updated daily.
